== Secret Wars Volume 2 ==

Khonshu Guardians
While in the Sewers, Rooftops or Bridge, this is in "wolf form" and gets +2 Attack.
Fight: KO one of your Heroes.
Attack: 3
VP: 1

Magma Men
Fight: KO one of your Heroes.
Fateful Resurrection
Attack: 3
VP: 1

Spider-Infected
